Interface Branch

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
Aclf3WXformer, AclfBranch, AcscBranch, Branch3W, DCLine2T, HvdcLine2T
All Known Implementing Classes:
Aclf3WXformerImpl, AclfBranchImpl, AcscBranchImpl, Branch3WImpl, BranchImpl, HvdcLine2TImpl
public interface Branch
extends ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel

A representation of the model object 'Branch'. Branch class for representing a Branch concept for power system simulation. The branch has two terminals, connecting to two buese.

The following features are supported:

  • Circuit Number
  • From Metered
  • Network
  • To Bus
  • From Bus
  • Dummy Bus List

java.lang.String getCircuitNumber()
